    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Art of writing, particularly the creation of beautiful, elegant letters or flourishes by hand with a pen, either in unjoined characters or in cursive writing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
